01:10:31.000 --> 01:10:37.000
and the main spheres that influence organizational behavior and organizational policy

01:10:38.000 --> 01:10:41.000
that the power in an organization carries out.

01:10:42.000 --> 01:10:50.000
When we studied the theory of leadership, you were able to remember three basic approaches to the theory of leadership.

01:10:51.000 --> 01:10:59.000
The earliest of them is the personal approach, which studied the qualities that distinguish leaders from non-leaders.

01:10:59.000 --> 01:11:04.000
It became the basis for further studies of the behavioral approach,

01:11:05.000 --> 01:11:12.000
when scientists studied behavioral models of leaders that distinguish them from non-leaders.

01:11:13.000 --> 01:11:18.000
And the most modern and perfect concept of the leadership approach

01:11:19.000 --> 01:11:22.000
we have recorded the models of situational leadership,

01:11:23.000 --> 01:11:27.000
which study not only the qualities and models of the behavior of the leader,

01:11:27.000 --> 01:11:33.000
but also the conditions, people and the structure of the task that the followers perform.

01:11:34.000 --> 01:11:40.000
We have also touched upon the concept of emotional intelligence in the modern study of leadership,

01:11:41.000 --> 01:11:46.000
which includes four main components, and contextual intelligence.
